/~*And +da synd uncl+ane +te heora cudu ne ceowa+d, for+dan +te hi getacnia+d +ta +de tela nella+d, ne nella+d leornian hw+at Gode leof sy, ne on heora mode wealcan +t+as h+alendes beboda, and syndon for+dy uncl+ane swa swa +da forcu+dan nytenu. "And those are unclean which chew not their cud, because they betoken those who desire not rightly, neither will learn what may be pleasing to God, nor revolve in their minds the Saviour's commands, and they are therefore unclean just like the wicked beasts. "
